	0% {

	100% {

  @keyframes blowUpContentTwo {

	  transform: scale(2);
	  opacity: 0;

	100% {
	  transform: scale(1);
	  opacity: 1;
	}
  }
  @keyframes blowUpModal {
	0% {
	  transform: scale(0);
	}
	100% {
	  transform: scale(1);
	}
  }
  @keyframes blowUpModalTwo {
	0% {
	  transform: scale(1);
	  opacity: 1;
	}
	50% {
		transform: scale(0.5);
		opacity: 0;
	  }
